<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About-Shortify</title>
    <style>
        /* Global Styles */
        body {
            font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a2a6c, #b21f1f, #fdbb2d);
            background-size: 400% 400%;
            color: #fff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            animation: gradientBG 15s ease infinite;
        }

        /* Background Gradient Animation */
        @keyframes gradientBG {
            0% {
                background-position: 0% 50%;
            }
            50% {
                background-position: 100% 50%;
            }
            100% {
                background-position: 0% 50%;
            }
        }

        /* Navbar */
      .navbar {
        background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
        padding: 10px 20px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        color: white;
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 1000;
      }

      .navbar .brand {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #fdbb2d;
      }

      .navbar ul {
        list-style: none;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        display: flex;
        gap: 20px;
        margin-left: auto;
      }

      .navbar ul li {
        display: inline-block;
      }

      .navbar ul li a {
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 8px 12px;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      }

      .navbar ul li a:hover {
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        border-radius: 5px;
      }

        /* About Page Styles */
        .about-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            padding: 0 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .about-container h1 {
            color: #fdbb2d;
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease-in-out;
        }

        .about-container p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #f0f0f0;
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out;
        }

        .about-container .highlight {
            color: #fdbb2d;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .about-container .button {
            padding: 12px 25px;
            background-color: #fdbb2d;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            color: #1a2a6c;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            animation: popIn 1.8s ease-in-out;
        }

        .about-container .button:hover {
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes popIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: scale(0.8);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .about-container h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

            .about-container p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            .about-container .button {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav class="navbar">
      <div class="brand">Shortify</div>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://shortify-n3ul.onrender.com/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://shortify-n3ul.onrender.com/logout">Logout</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://shortify-n3ul.onrender.com/admin/urls">Admin</a></li>
      </ul>
      <div class="hamburger" id="hamburger">
        <div></div>
        <div></div>
        <div></div>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="about-container">
        <h1>About Shortify</h1>
        <p>
            <span class="highlight">Shortify</span> is a modern URL shortening service that allows users to convert long, unwieldy links into short, easy-to-share URLs. 
            Whether you're sharing links with friends, posting on social media, or managing marketing campaigns, 
            Shortify makes your online presence simpler and cleaner.
        </p>
        <p>
            Our platform ensures that your shortened links are secure, reliable, and accessible. 
            With real-time tracking features and seamless integration with your workflow, 
            <span class="highlight">Shortify</span> is built for efficiency and performance.
        </p>
        <a href="/" class="button">Go Back to Home</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

